---
title: Chorizo, Pepper and Sweetcorn Naanizza with Balsamic Dressed Rocket
description: This Chorizo, Pepper and Sweetcorn Naanizza is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chorizo-pepper-and-sweetcorn-naanizza-4e43185a.jpg
